text: Michel Herbillon (born March 6, 1951) is a French politician. He is a member of The Republicans. He belongs to the National Assembly of France, representing the Val-de-Marne department. In the Republicans’ 2017 leadership election, Herbillon endorsed Laurent Wauquiez.Ludovic Vigogne (October 11, 2017), La liste des 136 parrains de Laurent Wauquiez L'Opinion. On 15 March 2020, Herbillon tested positive for COVID-19. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Île-de-France Category:People from Val-de-Marne
